Rulings.Base: 1. If you have multiple copies of this card in your hand, you can activate all of their effects in a Chain.\n2. If your 'Blackwing' monster is destroyed by battle and sent to the GY, you can still use this card's effect.\n3. If you control your opponent's monster at the end of the Damage Step, you cannot activate this card's effect because that monster is no longer "that opponent's monster" .
